Subject: Re: bug in kernel 2.6.21-rc1-git1: conventional floppy drive cannot   be mounted without hanging up the whole system
Sender: linux-kernel-owner@vger.kernel.org
Precedence: bulk
List-ID: <linux-kernel.vger.kernel.org>
